posting_body: ["If you're looking for a stunning 1BR or Studio apartment within minutes of some of the best scenic and happening places in Milwaukee look no further.", ' We are conveniently located posting_body: ['This is a 5 bedroom 2.5 bath single family home that has been used recently as a 4 bed AFH.', 'There are 4 bedrooms on the main floor along with a big kitchen, dining area, a handicap bathroom and half bath.', 'The hardwood floors have been refinished in the bedrooms, halls and living room.', 'On the second floor the is a very large carpeted bedroom with 3 closets a full bath and sitting area.', 'The basement is in three different sections, one has a large activity area, one has the laundry and mechanicals and the other one has a large storage area with shelving and an extra fridge.', 'There is a very large fenced in back yard, with a ADA ramp in the back and an electric wheel chair lift in the front.', 'There is tempered hot water and smoke alarms.', 'The garage is NOT part of the leased property.', 'The rent is $1,800.00 per month plus additional rent for taxes, water, sewer and insurance of approximately $700.00.', 'Tenant would also pay heat, electric, snow removal and grass cutting.', 'Please call Tony at', 'show contact info', 'for more info and to schedule a showing.']

posting_body: ['Beautiful historic fully-furnished 2 bedroom home located 3237 N.
